# Trivy ignore list — vulnerabilities we have explicitly evaluated and
# accept for now. Each entry must carry a brief justification so the
# next reviewer doesn't have to re-derive the decision.
#
# Format:
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN
#
# Empty by default. Add entries with comments above each one explaining
# why the vulnerability is accepted (e.g. "not exploitable without auth"
# or "fixed in upstream X but base image hasn't rebuilt yet").
